<div id="pf3881" class="pf w55 h235" data-page-no="3881"><div class="pc pc3881 w55 h235"><div class="t m137a x27 h104 y29c9 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">AVENUES TO </div><div class="t m692 x27 h104 y2bb9 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE SOUL </div><div class="t m400 xe5 h4e y29b5 ff3 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 2 </div><div class="t m1160 xe3 h35 y2ac3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">January 7-13 </div><div class="t m14db x165 hab y1e7c ff1 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">E.LEE  </div><div class="t m6a6 x3e h5 y14f6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Wherefore do ye spend money for </div><div class="t m690 xe h5 y165c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that which is not bread? and your labour </div><div class="t m635 xe h5 y16d4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for that which satisfieth not? hearken </div><div class="t m163f xe h5 y1e21 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">diligently unto me, and eat ye that which </div><div class="t ma30 xe h5 y1ee3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is good, and let your soul delight itself </div><div class="t m783 xe h5 y2172 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in fatness. Incline your ear, anal come </div><div class="t mcd3 xe h5 y1b73 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unto me: hear, and your soul shall live; </div><div class="t m964 xe h5 y1cb7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and I will make an everlasting covenant </div><div class="t m65a xe h5 y1905 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with you, even the sure mercies of </div><div class="t m713 xe h5 y2177 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">David.&quot; isa. 55:2, 3. </div><div class="t m791 x3e h35 y1d66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Effective communication includes lis-</div><div class="t mb49 x92 h35 y1b93 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tening, or receiving. In such communica-</div><div class="t m1b4 xe h35 y1a56 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion the recipient of the message makes </div><div class="t meda xe h35 y1b3d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">an intelligent use of the senses with which </div><div class="t m2a9 x92 h35 y1d68 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he is equipped. Communication fails </div><div class="t m3ef x92 h35 y167f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">when the listener offers neither attention </div><div class="t mdc9 x92 h35 y1aa0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nor interest. </div><div class="t m144 x3e h35 y650 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the Christian life the use we make </div><div class="t m658 xe h35 yb66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of our sensors—ears, eyes, hands, et </div><div class="t m425 xe h35 y2237 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cetera—may well determine both the </div><div class="t m639 x4 h35 y22fa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16  </div><div class="t m824 x5a h35 y1b22 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">depth of our spiritual experience and </div><div class="t m383 x5a h35 y165c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whether we shall be able to resist the wiles </div><div class="t m404 x5a h35 y1d58 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Satan as he seeks to delude God&apos;s chil-</div><div class="t m664 x5a h35 y2156 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dren. </div><div class="t m1a3a x56 h35 y1ee3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Our minds interpret impressions </div><div class="t m7b5 x5a h35 y2172 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">received through the senses. If these </div><div class="t m6ec x5a h35 y1b73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">senses are flooded with sensual or self-</div><div class="t m577 x5a h35 y1b75 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ishly oriented impressions, they will affect </div><div class="t ma3e x5a h35 y1905 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the course of life adversely. Patterns of </div><div class="t m180a x5a h35 y2177 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thought may develop which can be </div><div class="t m87f x5a h35 y1c7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">changed only by persistent effort con-</div><div class="t mae1 x5a h35 y1d66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trolled by the will. On the other hand, </div><div class="t m21f x5a h35 y1cb8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">impressions may build a basis for faith, </div><div class="t m6f x5a h35 y1a56 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the habits of Christian living be firmly </div><div class="t me8 x5a h35 y1e32 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">implanted in our life patterns. </div><div class="t m637 x56 h5 y1b7b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY PHRASES: </div><div class="t m89f xd2 h35 y167f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Obey my voice,&quot; </div><div class="t mf3c x5a h35 y1b7d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;hearken to me,&quot; these and many other </div><div class="t m771 x5a h35 yb65 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">similar Scripture commands remind us of </div><div class="t m719 x5a h35 y1153 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the importance of deliberately opening </div><div class="t ma00 x5a h35 y1ec0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our senses Godward. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
